</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>More Than 750,000 Could Lose Food Stamps Under Trump Administration Proposal</b>   <b data-is-speakable>The Trump administration has proposed changing food stamp  rules to require able-bodied adults without children to work 20 hours or more a week or lose benefits.  </b>
