    </div>
</div>
<div class="enlarge_html">
    <div class="image_data">
        <p class="caption">Alton Royal of Baltimore depends on food stamps but fears he will lose them under the proposed rule because he can't find a job.</p>
        <span class="credit" aria-label="Image credit">
            
            Pam Fessler/NPR
            
